{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You are the <strong>Servonauts</strong> - a team of dedicated, enthusiastic and utterly replaceable service station attendants. Work together with your friends to <strong>refine fuel</strong>, <strong>build pipelines</strong> and <strong>manage mayhem</strong> in many exotic locations throughout the galaxy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514400/extras/chaotic_and_colourful_madness_gif.gif?t=1739463758\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514400/extras/Headline_1.png?t=1739463758\" /><br>When cars pull into your servo, they\u2019ll request a specific kind of fuel. Build machines to refine this fuel, and combine fuels to make advanced recipes! But be careful - pumping the wrong fuel can have <strong>*explosive*</strong> consequences.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Astroil does not offer compensation for injuries related to employee mishaps.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514400/extras/work_hard_play_harder_gif.gif?t=1739463758\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514400/extras/Headline_2.png?t=1739463758\" /><br>To pump these cars, you\u2019ll need Astroil\u2019s patent-pending pipe technology! These wobbly, physically-simulated pipes can bend and stretch to get fuel where you need it. They\u2019re even partially lava-resistant (unlike the Servonauts)!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514400/extras/pump_your_way_to_the_top_gif.gif?t=1739463758\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514400/extras/Headline_3.png?t=1739463758\" /><br>Play in single-player with in-game support or grab your mates to jam it out as a duo, trio, or chaotic 4 player quartet. Work with your team and optimise your logistics as you aim to collect all three Gold Stars. Will this mean the Servonauts finally get a vacation? (Don\u2019t be ridiculous\u2026)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Game supports local couch coop and online via Steam Remote Play.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Are you Astroil's next Employee of the Month? Then get ready to launch!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Onboarded","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2514400/8b072cbff8262474904b0fc9849b4ebd17ff5aa9.jpg"},{"name":"Pit Crew","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2514400/a20cfb4181cf93244834a8ef0b9a390c4cc38406.jpg"},{"name":"Roadworkers","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2514400/5ef866de92df8f8370654a4c082acd52caed1237.jpg"},{"name":"Highwaymen","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2514400/082c65b49ef3eec3c80033fc0f6699c2ccc41084.jpg"},{"name":"Pitfliers","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2514400/e37a70eb4b085ec5a47a22c41144565d7d7b1c53.jpg"},{"name":"Abbreviators","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2514400/02ca53f38a79b6acf33cdf66bee71270af9e6747.jpg"},{"name":"Rusty Raviners","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2514400/19bdb20dbc21620e03bcf154ed5aa5ccecc5c8bb.jpg"},{"name":"Investigative Journalists","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2514400/2a172e15cf6526e95608dd3ae5dbe009cd76c171.